`8Keywords``   : Sweep
`8Categories`` : 
`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``

`8Syntax:`` 

 * sweep <victim>
 `` 

 This opening attack for warriors is intended to strike at multiple foes at
once, forcing them into melee combat with the warrior. Be advised however that
in the rage that goes with this sweep attack, you might attack friends and foes
alike. ``

